data.description: Welcome Home! This stunning Farmhouse, located in beautiful Hickory Hills, sits on a sprawling 1.45-acre lot, providing you with privacy and serenity. Step inside and be captivated by the beautiful pine floors that flow throughout the first floor, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The open floor plan is perfect for modern living and entertaining guests. The updated French doors with blinds bring in an abundance of natural light and provide easy access to the outdoor spaces. With 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, including a master bedroom on the main floor, there is plenty of room for your family and guests. The office den offers a quiet space to work or study. The custom kitchen is a chef's dream and features granite counters. Gather around the kitchen breakfast bar for casual dining or enjoy a more formal experience in the large dining room. Other notable features of this home include a wrap-around front porch where you can sit and enjoy the breathtaking views, a formal dining room for special occasions, and a large loft/family room upstairs for additional living space. The guest bedrooms are generously sized, and the jack and jill bathroom with dual sinks offers convenience for busy mornings. The garage is HUGE and has a large loft for storage as well as taller than average garage doors. The large backyard offers a platform/pergola for relaxing and watching the sunset. Additional RV parking has been added along with an electrical hookup for your RV guests. This home has a NEWER METAL ROOF! Don't miss your chance to own this magnificent waterfront home. Schedule a private tour today and experience luxurious living at its finest!
